/**
Write code that prompts the user for a phrase and a number of times to repeat it, then prints the phrase that
many times. Here is an example dialogue with the user:

What is your phrase? His name is Robert Paulson
How many times should I repeat it? 3
His name is Robert Paulson
His name is Robert Paulson
His name is Robert Paulson
 */

            // Declaration of Variables and Object
        Scanner userInput = new Scanner(System.in);
        int repeat;
            // Asking Questions and saving answers
        System.out.print("What is your phrase? ");
        String phrase = userInput.nextLine();
        System.out.print("How many times should I repeat it? ");
        repeat = userInput.nextInt();

        for(int i = 1; i <= repeat; i++)
            System.out.println(phrase);
